commit_message:
Map projects and roles per local match

Instead of defining projects and roles globally
for all local mapping matches, it should be on a
per match basis.

For example:

    "local": [
        {
            "user": {
                "name": "{0}"
            }
        },
        {
            "projects": [
                {
                    "name": "Project for {0}",
                    "roles": [
                        {
                            "name": "admin"
                        }
                    ]
                }
         }
    ]

Should be:

    "local": [
        {
            "user": {
                "name": "{0}"
            },
            {
                "projects": [
                    {
                        "name": "Project for {0}",
                        "roles": [
                            {
                                "name": "admin"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
             }
        }
    ]

Change-Id: Ib7b5b7f77708d48804e0913b67eab740f3674ac5
